These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, purple
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, parkour
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, begonia
2 different pets are kept: frog, turtle
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, subway
1. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
4. the owner of the frog is the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Game      | mah-jongg     | monopoly       |
| Color         | light-blue   | purple     |
| Job           | fisherman | mechanic   |
| Sport   | parkour   | skateboarding  |
| Flower   | begonia | amaryllis |
| Pet           | frog      | turtle     |
| Transport     | subway    | airplane   |

