2. the cape-cod house is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the german is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Flower      | marigold    | dahlia |
| Food         | nectarine        | strawberry  |
| Sport           | swimming | sailing  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Nationality   | australian     | german   |
| House           | palace         | cape-cod    |
| Transport     | tram           | van      |

